  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "Sometimes it feels like you're all alone Sometimes it feels like you can't go home Oh, sometimes it feels like the winter storm is always bearing down your door Gotta find the light, the direction out of your night And if you can't see it tonight, you just need to look clearer on your own Build up of you, the reframing of your own life here A new year in your own year, you gotta feel better about The diagonals, the hard edges, the shapes of your existence in this Perseverance of your own desires Sometimes it feels like tomorrow will never come The world's on your shoulders and you wish for Everyone just to get out without a harm But that's not the story no more, it all goes The black encompasses us, night lasts until the resurrection of Your dreams to you It's an allegorical metaphor for the whole thing, you know Sometimes you feel like you can't make it past that line And sometimes it feels like they'll never understand your mind Hold on to the little bit of light that you found Scratching away in the darkness of the brain that holds you here It's purpose is clear, you've got to I guess do whatever you want, that's the key to it all Can't fault you for that, just try not to hurt anyone Although that'll probably be hard Cause your feelings matter and someone else wants it a different way That's why you're all feeling entrapped Side alone cause you can't cut down your own wall Of making your life happy Thanks for watching!",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 28.280000686645508,
      "text": "Sometimes it feels like you're all alone Sometimes it feels like you can't go home",
      "start": 11
    },
    {
      "end": 42.279998779296875,
      "text": "Oh, sometimes it feels like the winter storm is always bearing down your door",
      "start": 30.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 52.119998931884766,
      "text": "Gotta find the light, the direction out of your night",
      "start": 43.70000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 64.16000366210938,
      "text": "And if you can't see it tonight, you just need to look clearer on your own",
      "start": 53.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 69.63999938964844,
      "text": "Build up of you, the reframing of your own life here",
      "start": 64.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 75.30000305175781,
      "text": "A new year in your own year, you gotta feel better about",
      "start": 69.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 82.16000366210938,
      "text": "The diagonals, the hard edges, the shapes of your existence in this",
      "start": 75.30000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 86.18000030517578,
      "text": "Perseverance of your own desires",
      "start": 83.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 94.5999984741211,
      "text": "Sometimes it feels like tomorrow will never come",
      "start": 87.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 100.31999969482422,
      "text": "The world's on your shoulders and you wish for",
      "start": 96.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 104.33999633789062,
      "text": "Everyone just to get out without a harm",
      "start": 100.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 109.27999877929688,
      "text": "But that's not the story no more, it all goes",
      "start": 104.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 117.27999877929688,
      "text": "The black encompasses us, night lasts until the resurrection of",
      "start": 109.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 121.27999877929688,
      "text": "Your dreams to you",
      "start": 118.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 127.62000274658203,
      "text": "It's an allegorical metaphor for the whole thing, you know",
      "start": 122.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 137.6199951171875,
      "text": "Sometimes you feel like you can't make it past that line",
      "start": 128.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 148.27999877929688,
      "text": "And sometimes it feels like they'll never understand your mind",
      "start": 139.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 156.47999572753906,
      "text": "Hold on to the little bit of light that you found",
      "start": 149.8000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 162.27999877929688,
      "text": "Scratching away in the darkness of the brain that holds you here",
      "start": 156.47999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 170.6199951171875,
      "text": "It's purpose is clear, you've got to",
      "start": 164.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 175.13999938964844,
      "text": "I guess do whatever you want, that's the key to it all",
      "start": 171.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 178.83999633789062,
      "text": "Can't fault you for that, just try not to hurt anyone",
      "start": 175.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 180.75999450683594,
      "text": "Although that'll probably be hard",
      "start": 178.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 184.39999389648438,
      "text": "Cause your feelings matter and someone else wants it a different way",
      "start": 180.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 188.5800018310547,
      "text": "That's why you're all feeling entrapped",
      "start": 184.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 193.5800018310547,
      "text": "Side alone cause you can't cut down your own wall",
      "start": 188.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 197.8000030517578,
      "text": "Of making your life happy",
      "start": 194.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 221.32000732421875,
      "text": "Thanks for watching!",
      "start": 221.24000549316406
    }
  ],
